<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<p>Given the initial coordinates, velocities, and accelerations of all the atoms at time 
 <italic>t</italic>, these parameters can be calculated by Velocity–Verlet algorithm [
 <xref rid="B36-nanomaterials-09-01617" ref-type="bibr">36</xref>] at time 
 <italic>t</italic> + Δ
 <italic>t</italic>, 
 <disp-formula id="FD4-nanomaterials-09-01617">
  <label>(4)</label>
  <math id="mm4">
   <mrow>
    <mrow>
     <mrow>
      <mo>{</mo>
      <mtable columnalign="left">
       <mtr>
        <mtd>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>r</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <mo>Δ</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>)</mo>
         <mo>=</mo>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>r</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>)</mo>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>v</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>)</mo>
         <mo>Δ</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <mfrac>
          <mn>1</mn>
          <mn>2</mn>
         </mfrac>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>a</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>)</mo>
         <mo>Δ</mo>
         <msup>
          <mi>t</mi>
          <mn>2</mn>
         </msup>
        </mtd>
       </mtr>
       <mtr>
        <mtd>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>v</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <mo>Δ</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>)</mo>
         <mo>=</mo>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>v</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>)</mo>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>a</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>)</mo>
         <mo>Δ</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
        </mtd>
       </mtr>
       <mtr>
        <mtd>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>a</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <mo>Δ</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>)</mo>
         <mo>=</mo>
         <mo>−</mo>
         <mfrac>
          <mn>1</mn>
          <mi>m</mi>
         </mfrac>
         <mo>∇</mo>
         <mi>U</mi>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal">
          <mi>r</mi>
         </mstyle>
         <mo>(</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mo>+</mo>
         <mo>Δ</mo>
         <mi>t</mi>
         <mrow>
          <mo>)</mo>
          <mo>)</mo>
         </mrow>
        </mtd>
       </mtr>
      </mtable>
     </mrow>
    </mrow>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula> where Δ
 <italic>t</italic> is time step, 
 <bold>r</bold> is coordinate vector, 
 <bold>v</bold> is velocity vector, 
 <bold>a</bold> is acceleration vector, and 
 <italic>m</italic> is mass of an atom.
</p>
